             was indicted for <rs id="t18200112-19-off105" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200112-19-off105" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200112-19-off105" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200112-19-cd106" type="crimeDate">7th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-19-off105 t18200112-19-cd106"></join>, two knife-rests, value 10 s., and one ring, value 20 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18200112-19-victim199" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Barnard
                  <interp inst="t18200112-19-victim199" type="surname" value="Barnard"></interp>
